Paper: hep-th/9903180

Date: 1999-03-22

Title: A critique of the gauge technique

Comments: 18 pages, Latex. To appear in Aust. J. Phys

Journal-ref: Austral.J.Phys. 52 (1999) 681-695

A summary of the successes of and obstacles to the gauge technique (anon-perturbative method of solving Dyson-Schwinger equations in gauge theories)is given, as well as an outline of how progress may be achieved in this field.